text: Elkton High School is a high school located in Elkton, Maryland, United States on 110 James St. It is a member of the Cecil County Public Schools and there are approximately 990 students. ==Notable alumni== * Nick Hodge, financial author and commentator * Niles Scott, National Football League player * Larry Webster, former National Football League player ==References== ==External links== * Category:Public high schools in Maryland Category:Schools in Cecil County, Maryland Category:Elkton, Maryland Category:Educational institutions established in 1958 Category:1958 establishments in Maryland
title: Elkton High School (Maryland)
